Ansible Role for AWS tools

If you want to install only a set of tools, you need to edit the mail.yaml file.

Dry-Run the playbook on Amazon Linux group 
 * ansible-playbook -i hosts aws-tools-amazonlinux.yml --check

Run the playbook on Centos group
 * ansible-playbook -i hosts aws-tools-centos.yml

Run the playbook on Ubuntu group
 * ansible-playbook -i hosts aws-tools-ubuntu.yml
